        "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\n> Why isn't there a set of CI Jenkins jobs for Gizmo?\n > \n > Without the Verify job the code cannot be submitted.\n\nGizmo depends on the event library (which is a library that hasn't yet been ported to ONAP), and won't build until that exists.  Both Gizmo and the Event library are part of Beijing. CI jobs will be created when Gizmo is buildable.  In the mean time, we need to get the seed code into ONAP.",
